#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:16
msgid ""
"Corona advice, Women’s Day, a landmark legal victory against airport "
"expansion, and lots more updates and news from the global Rebellion."
msgstr ""
"新冠疫情下的建议、国际妇女节与反机场扩张的一次标志性的胜利……反叛灭绝为您带来"
"全球最新消息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:18
msgid "![image1](/assets/uploads/2020-03-13-newsletter-37-image1.jpg)"
msgstr "![image1](/assets/uploads/2020-03-13-newsletter-37-image1.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:20
msgid "Dearest Rebels,"
msgstr "亲爱的反叛者们,"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:22
msgid ""
"This issue, we celebrate the incredible courage and kindness of [women "
"everywhere](https://subscribe.organise.earth/archive/4VKY8G3o/94Beob9D/"
"Asln9ADL?locale=en-US%27), from the Republic of Congo to the bridges of "
"London, who are standing strong to **honour each other and the Earth**."
msgstr ""
"今天我们想赞美 [世界各地的女人们](https://subscribe.organise.earth/"
"archive/4VKY8G3o/94Beob9D/Asln9ADL?locale=en-US%27)无处不在的勇气和善意, 从刚"
"果共和国到伦敦塔桥，她们都在勇敢 **为彼此和地球奔走呐喊**."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:24
msgid ""
"If you haven’t already, check out [this powerful video](https://youtu.be/"
"s5AAscy7qbI) **of women performing the protest dance** called **‘Un Violador "
"en Tu Camino’ (A Rapist in Your Path)** for **International Women’s Day.**"
msgstr ""
"点开 [这个视频](https://youtu.be/s5AAscy7qbI) **女人们选择用一支** 名叫 "
"**‘Un Violador en Tu Camino’ (你前路里的强奸犯)** 的舞蹈来纪念今年的 **国际妇"
"女节。**"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:26
msgid "![](/assets/uploads/2020-03-13-newsletter-37-image2.jpg)"
msgstr "![](/assets/uploads/2020-03-13-newsletter-37-image2.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:28
msgid ""
"We take time to consider the very **serious and ongoing threat that "
"Coronavirus (Covid-19) poses to our activities and the planned** [Waves of "
"Rebellion](https://m.facebook.com/story.php?"
"story_fbid=491848371504101&id=239675493315233&refsrc=https://m.facebook.com/"
"watch/&_rdr). Rebels have been working tirelessly to find a path which seeks "
"to protect life, support the most vulnerable, and draw our communities "
"together in a time of crisis."
msgstr ""
"我们正在衡量 **当前形势严峻的新冠肺炎对现存活动和将来** [反叛浪潮](https://m."
"facebook.com/story.php?"
"story_fbid=491848371504101&id=239675493315233&refsrc=https://m.facebook.com/"
"watch/&_rdr) 的负面影响. 反抗者们也正不遗余力地寻找一条能在危机面前保护生命、"
"支持那些最脆弱的个体并将我们的社区凝聚在一起的路。"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:30
msgid ""
"‘Business as usual’ has been disrupted with a shocking jolt, and people "
"everywhere are called on to do what we can to slow the progress of this "
"pandemic."
msgstr ""
"正常的生产经营活动已经受到了冲击，世界各地的人们也都紧随号召抵抗着这次大流行"
"的冲击。"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Advice from healthcare professionals and experts is to limit social contact and self-isolate to slow the spread of Coronavirus. Rebels are encouraged to hold meetings online wherever possible, and to think carefully before organising in-person gatherings.**\n"
msgstr "**卫生专家建人们通过减少社交接触、保持个人隔离来控制疫情蔓延。反叛者们也开始尽可能地采用线上会议，在组织人群聚集活动时也是思虑再三。**\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Slowing this virus down will make a big difference to how well we can care for people who are affected. By limiting our contact with others, where possible, we can relieve unnecessary strain on healthcare providers and save lives.** \n"
msgstr "**降低疫情的蔓延速度对帮助那些受其影响的人至关重要。无论何时何地，减少和他人的接触都能减轻医护人员的压力，挽救生命。** \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "**As rebels, we can choose to engage with and support our local communities in this crisis. This is an opportunity to prefigure the world we want to build: one that chooses life and regeneration over despair and fear.**\n"
msgstr "**作为反叛者们，我们选择用实际行动支持当地社区度过这次危机——这是一次危机，也是一次机会，可以展现出我们想建立的那个世界：在那里，人们总是会选择生命和新生，而不是绝望和恐惧。**\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:38
msgid ""
"Read the [global XR response](https://docs.google.com/document/"
"d/1DfwBGrgeI4DJfnIExBAlnTVLJODJ16-2cVDQp7YF3Os/edit?usp=sharing) to the "
"CoronaVirus ([UK update here](https://rebellion.earth/2020/03/12/extinction-"
"rebellion-uk-on-the-may-rebellion-and-coronavirus/)), join the [Community "
"Action Telegram broadcast group](https://t.me/XRCoronaCA) for the latest "
"info, and check out [the WHO advice](https://www.who.int/emergencies/"
"diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019) for more details on how to protect yourself "
"and others."
msgstr ""
"点击阅读 [反叛灭绝全球在行动](https://docs.google.com/document/"
"d/1DfwBGrgeI4DJfnIExBAlnTVLJODJ16-2cVDQp7YF3Os/edit?usp=sharing) 应对新冠肺"
"炎 ([来自英国的最新消息](https://rebellion.earth/2020/03/12/extinction-"
"rebellion-uk-on-the-may-rebellion-and-coronavirus/)), 加入 [社区行动电报广播"
"小组](https://t.me/XRCoronaCA) 收听最新消息，点击查看[世卫组织的建议]"
"(https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019) 看看如何能"
"更好地保护自己和他人。"

