#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:44
msgid ""
"Elsewhere in today’s issue, **XR Italy kicks off the wave of rebellion** "
"with some beautiful disruption at the Venice Carnival. Who knew blindfolds, "
"lock on’s, and dancing went so well together?"
msgstr ""
"**反抗灭绝意大利小分队** 近日在威尼斯狂欢节开展了一次活动。谁能想到眼罩、锁和"
"舞蹈能如此完美地融合在一起呢？"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:46
msgid ""
"Also, we turn to Canada which has seen widespread civil disobedience for "
"over a month now, initiated by the **indigenous Wet'suwet'en chiefs**, in "
"[protest of a multi-billion-dollar pipeline](https://www.thenation.com/"
"article/activism/indigenous-resistance-wetsuweten-canada/)."
msgstr ""
"与此同时，加拿大成员们的活动已经开展了一个多月，此次活动由**indigenous "
"Wet'suwet'en chiefs**发起, 旨在抗议 [一条价值数十亿美元的管道](https://www."
"thenation.com/article/activism/indigenous-resistance-wetsuweten-canada/)."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:48
msgid ""
"We catch up with **rebels in Hong Kong** who are rising like the hungry "
"seas, and take a look at the **recent victory in the UK** - where the "
"Heathrow airport expansion plans have been [deemed illegal](https://www."
"theguardian.com/environment/2020/feb/27/heathrow-third-runway-ruled-illegal-"
"over-climate-change) on the foundation of the Paris Agreement."
msgstr ""
"**香港的反叛者们** 一哄而起的同时，**我们最近在英国也取得了胜利** - 在那里，"
"希思罗机场的扩建计划刚刚因巴黎协定而 [被判非法](https://www.theguardian.com/"
"environment/2020/feb/27/heathrow-third-runway-ruled-illegal-over-climate-"
"change) 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-03-13-newsletter-37.md:50
msgid ""
"In our [XR Unchained](https://rebellion.earth/2020/03/13/xr-unchained-13/) "
"this month, you’ll find an **barrage of rebellious ingenuity from around the "
"world**, including-but-not-limited-to: umbrella protests in **Indonesia**, "
"oil-rig hopping in **New Zealand**, and further rumblings in **Russia!**"
msgstr ""
"在本月的[XR Unchained](https://rebellion.earth/2020/03/13/xr-unchained-13/) "
"里，你会看到 **来自世界各地的一连串的反叛活动**，包括但不限于 **印度尼西亚"
